node.text:
JULlAN DID IT! 🏄‍♂️

We celebrate that our kids are companions but you are mine. Sharing parenthood with you is my greatest joy and I am so thankful we are on this journey together❤ 🤙Happy Father's Day to our problem solver. The point and clicker. The hard decision maker. The reassurer. The most efficient there is, and 100% the fun one. We love you❤
.
.
#1Dad #fathersday #bestdad #magic
